<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.6.9">
<l>nilaiyāḷā niṉvaṇaṅka vēṇṭāyē yākilumeṉ</l>
<l>mulaiyāḷa vorunāḷuṉ ṉakalattā lāḷāyē</l>
<l>cilaiyāḷā marameyta tiṟalāḷā tirumeyya</l>
<l>malaiyāḷā nīyāḷa vaḷaiyāḷa māṭṭōmē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even if you do not need [me] to worship you as [your] steadfast servant,</l>
<l>Someday, you [must] receive [me] with your chest to control my breasts;</l>
<l>Bowman, you who used strength to shoot the trees,</l>
<l rend="indent">man of Tirumeyya mountain,</l>
<l>When you rule, we will not be able to rule [our] bangles.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
